OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright to start in the east but
OL,6,Fsoon clouding over as rain continues
OL,7,Fto spread eastwards. Behind it, sunny
OL,8,Fspells and frequent blustery showers,
OL,9,Fthese heavy at times and falling
OL,10,Fwintry over the hills. Coastal gales
OL,11,Fin the north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain continues to clear the
OL,14,Fsoutheast, with blustery showers
OL,15,Fpersisting, especially in the
OL,16,Fnorthwest. These easing in the south
OL,17,Fby dawn with clear spells in between.
OL,18,FTurning chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
