OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FScattered showers to start,
OL,6,Fthen cloud building with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading across the country,
OL,8,Fthough mostly dry in the far
OL,9,Fsoutheast. Breezy, especially along
OL,10,Fthe hills and coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
